             was indicted for <rs id="t18160710-32-off150" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160710-32-off150" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160710-32-off150" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160710-32-cd151" type="crimeDate">20th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160710-32-off150 t18160710-32-cd151"></join>, two pieces of linen dowlas, value 4s. and a shilling
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18160710-32-victim261" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Rothwell
                  <interp inst="t18160710-32-victim261" type="surname" value="Rothwell"></interp>
